<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dawn-vi">dawn <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɔːn/    美 /dɔːn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>破晓；被理解：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The day dawned calmly.
黎明悄然而至。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It dawned on</strong> me <strong>that</strong> Jo had been right all along.
我开始明白了乔一直都是对的。</p></div></div>